          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1639996104950-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Place the <strong>curried basa fillets </strong>on top of the vegetables</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a further 14-15 min or until the fish is cooked through, the potatoes are crisp and the vegetables have softened – this is your <strong>curried basa tray bake</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1639996108540-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1639996108540-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
